languages.text: "Как и я, прекрасный ангел, как и я! Впрочем, я и твое имя слышала лишь мельком и жалею, что судьба не свела нас раньше..."
"Neither have I, my sweet angel, neither have I! But then again, I've barely heard your name, and I regret that fate didn't bring us together sooner..."

languages.text: “我也没有，我可爱的天使，我也没有！但话说回来，我以前也没听说过你的名字。真遗憾，要是命运能让我更早遇见你就好了……”

languages.text: «¡Ni yo tampoco, mi dulce ángel, ni yo tampoco! Aunque apenas he oído el tuyo y ya lamento que el destino no nos uniera antes...».
languages.original_text: "Neither have I, my sweet angel, neither have I! But then again, I've barely heard your name, and I regret that fate didn't bring us together sooner..."

traits.locale_text: «¡Ni yo tampoco, mi dulce ángel, ni yo tampoco! Aunque apenas he oído el tuyo y ya lamento que el destino no nos uniera antes...».

languages.text: 「あたしも初めて聞いたわ、可愛い天使様！とはいえ、あなたの名前もほとんど聞いたことがなかったの。運命がもっと早くあたしたちを引き合わせてくれていたならって、日々後悔しているわ…」
languages.original_text: "Neither have I, my sweet angel, neither have I! But then again, I've barely heard your name, and I regret that fate didn't bring us together sooner..."

traits.locale_text: 「あたしも初めて聞いたわ、可愛い天使様！とはいえ、あなたの名前もほとんど聞いたことがなかったの。運命がもっと早くあたしたちを引き合わせてくれていたならって、日々後悔しているわ…」

languages.text: "Ich auch nicht, mein süßer Engel, ich auch nicht! Aber Euren Namen kenne ich ja auch kaum, und ich bedauere, dass uns das Schicksal nicht früher zusammengeführt hat ..."
languages.original_text: "Neither have I, my sweet angel, neither have I! But then again, I've barely heard your name, and I regret that fate didn't bring us together sooner..."

languages.text: « Moi non plus, mon ange, moi non plus ! Bon, après, je n'avais jamais entendu le vôtre non plus, et je regrette que le destin ne nous ait pas rassemblées plus tôt... »

languages.text: "Ben de tatlı meleğim, ben de! Gerçi senin adını da çok duymamıştım. Kaderin yollarımızı daha erken kesiştirmemiş oluşu beni kahrediyor."

traits.locale_text: "Ben de öyle balım, ben de öyle! Gerçi senin adını da çok duymamıştım ama kader yollarımızı daha erken kesiştirmedi diye kahroluyorum."
